Class MrzScanPlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.anyline.plugin.AbstractScanPlugin<ScanResult<Identification>>
      • io.anyline.plugin.mrz.MrzScanPlugin
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ScanPlugin<ScanResult<Identification>>

    public class MrzScanPlugin
extends AbstractScanPlugin<ScanResult<Identification>>

    Anyline MRZ plugin

    The Anyline MRZ plugin scans the machine readable zones from passports and other ids.

    This plugin is in ALPHA state and may change in a future version.
